s:2988:"<h1><strong>📢 ANNOUNCEMENT: AcemyX Leaderboard Rewards Are Here! 🏆</strong></h1>
<p>Dear Student,</p>
<p>We're excited to introduce <strong>Leaderboard Rewards</strong> to <strong>motivate and recognize your efforts</strong> on the platform! 🎉 Now, <strong>every action you take on AcemyX</strong>—from studying to participating in discussions—earns you points, and the top performers get <strong>amazing rewards</strong>!</p>
<hr />
<h2><strong>🏅 How the Leaderboard Works</strong></h2>
<p>🔹 You <strong>earn points</strong> for various activities, such as:<br />✔️ <strong>Starting discussions</strong> in the forum.<br />✔️ <strong>Posting helpful content</strong> in the forum.<br />✔️ <strong>Submitting feedback</strong> on courses.<br />✔️ <strong>Checking out course pages &amp; completing lessons.</strong></p>
<p>💡 <strong>The more you engage, the higher you rank!</strong></p>
<hr />
<h2><strong>🏆 Leaderboard Rewards (Monthly Prizes!)</strong></h2>
<p>🥇 <strong>Top 3 Students Each Month Receive:</strong><br />🎖 <strong>Leaderboard Recognition</strong> – Your name will be displayed on the <strong>Hall of Fame</strong> as one of AcemyX’s top students!<br />🎖 <strong>Bonus Leaderboard Points</strong> – Earn extra points to <strong>stay ahead of the competition.</strong><br />🎖 <strong>Subscription Discounts:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>🥈 <strong>1st Runner-up:</strong> <strong>20% off</strong> their next subscription!</li>
<li>🥉 <strong>2nd Runner-up:</strong> <strong>10% off</strong> their next subscription!<br />🎖 <strong>Half-Month Course Access Extension</strong> – The <strong>highest performer</strong> of the month gets <strong>an extra 2 weeks of free access</strong> to their course!</li>
</ul>
<p>📢 <strong>Your hard work deserves to be celebrated! Start participating now to secure your spot at the top.</strong></p>
<hr />
<h2><strong>🔥 Special Bonus: Win Twice, Get a Free Data Subscription! 🎉</strong></h2>
<p>📌 <strong>If you win the Leaderboard Top Performer reward two times in a row, you will receive a free data subscription!</strong><br />📌 <strong>The counting starts fresh after each win, so you always have a chance to earn this special reward!</strong></p>
<p>💡 <strong>The more you refer, the more you benefit! Keep climbing the leaderboard, and stay ahead of the competition!</strong></p>
<hr />
<h2><strong>🔥 How to Get Started?</strong></h2>
<p>➡️ <strong>Engage with courses, post in forums, and complete lessons.</strong><br />➡️ <strong>Check the leaderboard regularly to track your progress.</strong><br />➡️ <strong>Aim to be in the Top 3 for a chance to win rewards!</strong></p>
<p>🏆 <strong>Will YOU be AcemyX’s next top student?</strong> Let’s find out! 🚀</p>
<p><strong>Start earning points today!</strong></p>
<p>📌 <em>Stay tuned for updates &amp; keep an eye on your leaderboard rank!</em></p>";